TARANTULUS hissed as he stood up, "How dare you question my knowledge
and ability." His optics were darkening with anger. "We are dealing
with something far more than just a doorway. We are dealing with a
tear, one that grows as long as we stay here on this ball of dirt."

SKYSHADOW was also listening intently as ANTAGONY spoke, a he found
this interesting and somewhat unsettling. The doorway made him
uncomfortable enough, but a tear? Then he looked around as he noted
several missing figures, one was FRACTYL who might have some
infromation on this , but also HYDRAS' most loyal soldier INFERNO.

The ebony colored ANTAGONY crossed her arms casually over her chest,
"There is something that may stop it." Her tone dark and vaguely
dissmissive of TARANTULUS, but carefully hidden. "It is called a
Zeta-Hypercube."

(TAG)

- Preston
